parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag sensor can cause the airbag light to stay on, indicating a potential safety risk, and may prevent the airbag from deploying in the event of an accident, which can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: the airbag sensor fails to detect occupancy
the airbag may not deploy in the event of an accident
and the passenger airbag sensor may not turn off when a passenger is in the seat.
